 202â†’ *
 203â†’ * Actions:
 204â†’ * - Download: Downloads file from IPFS, decrypts, and triggers browser download
 205â†’ * - Rename: Opens dialog to rename file/folder
 206â†’ * - Delete: Shows confirmation, then removes from folder metadata
 207â†’ * - Move: Drag-drop to folder rows in list
 208â†’ *
 209â†’ * @example
 210â†’ * ```tsx
 211â†’ * function FilesPage() {
 212â†’ *   return (
 213â†’ *     <main className="app-main">
 214â†’ *       <FileBrowser />
 215â†’ *     </main>
 216â†’ *   );
 217â†’ * }
 218â†’ * ```
