  1â†’/**
  2â†’ * File Metadata Service - Per-file IPNS operations
  3â†’ *
  4â†’ * Creates, resolves, and updates per-file IPNS metadata records.
  5â†’ * Each file gets its own IPNS record containing encrypted metadata,
