231â†’/**
232â†’ * Determine whether a file content update should create a new version entry.
233â†’ *
234â†’ * - If `forceVersion` is true, always returns true (web re-upload always versions).
235â†’ * - If no versions exist yet, returns true (first version always created).
236â†’ * - If the newest version is older than VERSION_COOLDOWN_MS, returns true.
237â†’ * - If the newest version is within cooldown, returns false (overwrite without versioning).
238â†’ *
239â†’ * @param currentMetadata - Current file metadata (may have existing versions)
240â†’ * @param forceVersion - Whether to force version creation (e.g., explicit re-upload)
241â†’ * @returns true if a new version entry should be created
